0a224575-1943-4fec-bc54-bf531018fd03.description: As long as the challenge has not started the player can build their creation here.
0a224575-1943-4fec-bc54-bf531018fd03.title: Build Platform

2855df9b-8684-44ae-aaa8-8df0f96dbef6.description: A frame with an arrow that lights up when triggered.
2855df9b-8684-44ae-aaa8-8df0f96dbef6.title: Ball Spawner Frame Two

3da9c71f-9900-48a2-be66-8d1c80f88ac8.description: This block will finish a challenge when triggered. It's useful if you want your challenge to end with a switch, sensor or button activation.
3da9c71f-9900-48a2-be66-8d1c80f88ac8.title: Goal Block

43562d7c-d1a8-4cea-98e0-ad791320729b.description: Build on the lift to create freely movable constructions that won't be fixed to the ground. Can be elevated and lowered as well as lift creations that have flipped over.
43562d7c-d1a8-4cea-98e0-ad791320729b.title: Lift

4a9929e9-aa85-4791-89c2-f8799920793f.description: The Challenge Starter allows you to create challenges that does not require a creation to trigger the goal. Needs to be connected to a trigger to start the challenge.
4a9929e9-aa85-4791-89c2-f8799920793f.title: Challenge Starter

5929670a-fe70-40a7-83e4-45cf179b0aef.description: Used to communicate challenge logic to the player.
5929670a-fe70-40a7-83e4-45cf179b0aef.title: On / Off Light Block

61b85d08-4087-4d7c-9ddb-64caeb60e447.description: The Character Spawner lets you spawn characters from Survival mode in your challenges. Connect it to a trigger or the Challenge starter to spawn the selected character.
61b85d08-4087-4d7c-9ddb-64caeb60e447.title: Character Spawner

6ca42dd6-0f2f-4abe-9aee-e1acb2bfcf40.description: Gives an overview of the challenge.
6ca42dd6-0f2f-4abe-9aee-e1acb2bfcf40.title: Map Computer

7bbf53fd-2b5e-4717-9b9c-ba8962b611e1.description: Bringing your creation over this Goal Platform wins the challenge. Connect an input to set a win condition. Connect outputs to trigger celebration events.
7bbf53fd-2b5e-4717-9b9c-ba8962b611e1.title: Goal Platform

8684ad89-94ad-4f46-b50e-c1aff63893f4.description: Senses creations and players in front of it. 64 block range. Senses through walls.
8684ad89-94ad-4f46-b50e-c1aff63893f4.title: Big Sensor

8ec1120b-b272-44e8-9ad2-5b1998cb2477.description: A frame with an arrow that lights up when triggered.
8ec1120b-b272-44e8-9ad2-5b1998cb2477.title: Ball Spawner Frame One

90109b86-3dcf-44b3-a8e1-28c37122d5a7.description: Bringing your creation over this Goal Platform wins the challenge. Connect an input to set a win condition. Connect outputs to trigger celebration events.
90109b86-3dcf-44b3-a8e1-28c37122d5a7.title: Small Goal Platform

945d6152-fc82-48ec-a113-3896c14e8c5f.description: Connect to a trigger and activate to start the celebration!
945d6152-fc82-48ec-a113-3896c14e8c5f.title: Celebrationbot

9b9e4547-0846-42da-b812-9f1a5b22e52f.description: Connect in a series to light up a path.
9b9e4547-0846-42da-b812-9f1a5b22e52f.title: Arrow Light Block

af130ba7-f0ed-4a5a-97f8-be78b54e972b.description: Spawns a ball when the challenge starts. Connect to a trigger to control the spawning. A new one will spawn if the ball falls off the edge.
af130ba7-f0ed-4a5a-97f8-be78b54e972b.title: Ball Spawner

b3402155-e8a3-452d-b6fb-55c8d4e4e681.description: Fill with the items you want the player to build with in your challenge.
b3402155-e8a3-452d-b6fb-55c8d4e4e681.title: Challenge Chest

b5858089-b1f8-4d13-a485-fdaa204d9c6b.description: Players will start on these when playing the challenge.
b5858089-b1f8-4d13-a485-fdaa204d9c6b.title: Player Start

badc4d45-1b75-4528-9451-a46270189190.description: Bring a ball of matching color into the socket to activate.
badc4d45-1b75-4528-9451-a46270189190.title: Ball Socket

dcbab714-d981-4998-9b90-5332e36d3632.description:
They love you!
Perfect for celebrating the completion of a challenge.
dcbab714-d981-4998-9b90-5332e36d3632.title: Pop-up Audience

dff53b11-2d8d-4044-ad51-59321f117f8e.description: A really long and powerful piston useful for moving large doors and platforms in challenges.
dff53b11-2d8d-4044-ad51-59321f117f8e.title: Big Piston

fa9de66b-fd92-4d67-bf68-6584937b736d.description: Spawns an explosive canister when the challenge starts. Connect to a trigger to control the spawning. A new one will spawn if the canister is destroyed.
fa9de66b-fd92-4d67-bf68-6584937b736d.title: Explosive Canister Spawner

fc3b1e92-1e81-45cf-9cbc-7ddb85604ff6.description: Takes notes whenever the player builds something.
fc3b1e92-1e81-45cf-9cbc-7ddb85604ff6.title: Observerbot

55abf9f8-5fd5-44c9-bd1e-207ca3bb9864.description: Gives you access to the challenge mode pause menu
55abf9f8-5fd5-44c9-bd1e-207ca3bb9864.title: Menu
